{"tid":2406980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真正嘅男權師","createTime":"2021-02-13T15:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T16:09:41.000Z","uid":358948,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"641d9e0ecd27fa45752d716554a84c9ae09b7d17","tid":2406980,"uid":358948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"係長毛梁國雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n懲教署本月起　已要求女囚犯須剪髮<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄2014年入獄時被剪去已及腰的長髮，他質疑懲教署剪髮規定只限男囚犯，惟女囚犯卻可留長髮並不公平，故提出司法覆核。案件經原審及上訴，去年11月才獲終極勝訴，終審法院認為，懲教署要求男性剪短頭髮的規定違反《性別歧視條例》，下令署方須取消有關措施。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvuk3Wj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffvuk3Wj.jpg&h=20709d71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c3b67d51a4c1a372c5810c1b887fb26af7cb28d","tid":2406980,"uid":358948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T16:09:41.000Z","msg":"屌你！邊隻臭雞女權比負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}